{"id":1208,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":169,"title":"Conversation 89","subtitle":"Grocery Store Checkout Conversation","level":"A2","parts":14,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-89.1208/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/0-conversation-89.mp3","transcript":"Welcome to Cosmos.\nIs there anything I can help you with?\nNo, thank you.\nI was looking for a particular brand of milk that I normally buy,\nbut I couldn't find it.\nLuckily, a stock clerk helped me with that.\nGreat.\nWell, I'll go ahead and ring up your purchase.\nOkay... Your total comes to $49.80.\nOh, I'd like to use the coupon that came with the promotional brochure.\nNo problem.\nHere, let me just scan the barcode.\nYou should be able to see the new total on the screen.\nLooks good, thanks a lot.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:01:04","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Welcome to Cosmos.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/1.mp3","time_start":0.13,"time_end":2.1},{"position":2,"content":"Is there anything I can help you with?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/2.mp3","time_start":2.1,"time_end":4.22},{"position":3,"content":"No, thank you.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/3.mp3","time_start":4.47,"time_end":5.52},{"position":4,"content":"I was looking for a particular brand of milk that I normally buy,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/4.mp3","time_start":5.52,"time_end":9.12},{"position":5,"content":"but I couldn't find it.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/5.mp3","time_start":9.12,"time_end":10.69},{"position":6,"content":"Luckily, a stock clerk helped me with that.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/6.mp3","time_start":10.8,"time_end":13.81},{"position":7,"content":"Great.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/7.mp3","time_start":13.93,"time_end":14.78},{"position":8,"content":"Well, I'll go ahead and ring up your purchase.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/8.mp3","time_start":14.95,"time_end":18.01},{"position":9,"content":"Okay... Your total comes to $49.80.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/9.mp3","time_start":18.01,"time_end":23.01},{"position":10,"content":"Oh, I'd like to use the coupon that came with the promotional brochure.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/10.mp3","time_start":23.01,"time_end":27.51},{"position":11,"content":"No problem.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/11.mp3","time_start":27.71,"time_end":29.02},{"position":12,"content":"Here, let me just scan the barcode.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/12.mp3","time_start":29.12,"time_end":32.01},{"position":13,"content":"You should be able to see the new total on the screen.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/13.mp3","time_start":32.11,"time_end":35.25},{"position":14,"content":"Looks good, thanks a lot.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-89-2023-09-30-22-47-04/14.mp3","time_start":35.25,"time_end":37.37}]}